isas%20in%20India%20will%20provide%20easier%20access%20to%20visas%20with%20multi-year%20validity%20for%20travellers%20with%20an%20established%20travel%20history%2C%20if%20the%20passport%20validity%20allows%2C%20the%20EU%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20on%20April%2018%20adopted%20specific%20rules%20on%20issuing%20multiple%20entry%20visas%20to%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20which%20are%20more%20favourable%20than%20the%20standard%20rules%20of%20the%20Visa%20Code%20that%20applied%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newly%20adopted%20visa%20%26quot%3Bcascade%26quot%3B%20regime%20for%20India%2C%20Indian%20nationals%20can%20now%20be%20issued%20long-term%2C%20multi-entry%20Schengen%20visas%20valid%20for%20two%20years%20after%20having%20obtained%20and%20lawfully%20used%20two%20visas%20within%20the%20previous%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-year%20visa%20will%20normally%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20five-year%20visa%2C%20if%20the%20passport%20has%20sufficient%20validity%20remaining.%20During%20the%20validity%20period%20of%20these%20visas%2C%20holders%20enjoy%20travel%20rights%20equivalent%20to%20visa-free%20nationals%2C%20the%20EU%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20comes%20in%20the%20context%20of%20strengthened%20relations%20under%20the%20EU-India%20Common%20Agenda%20on%20Migration%20and%20Mobility%2C%20which%20seeks%20comprehensive%20cooperation%20on%20migration%20policy%20between%20the%20EU%20and%20India%2C%20with%20facilitation%20of%20people-to-people%20contacts%20being%20of%20key%20aspect%20due%20to%20the%20importance%20of%20India%20as%20a%20partner%20for%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchengen%20visas%20allow%20the%20holder%20to%20travel%20freely%20in%20the%20Schengen%20area%20for%20short%20stays%20of%20a%20maximum%20of%2090%20days%20in%20any%20180-day%20period.%20The%20visas%20are%20not%20purpose-bound%2C%20but%20they%20do%20not%20grant%20the%20right%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Schengen%20area%2