26quot%3BNot%20just%20MDH%20and%20Everest%2C%20samples%20will%20be%20taken%20from%20all%20the%20spice%20manufacturing%20companies.%20The%20report%20will%20come%20from%20the%20lab%20in%20about%2020%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Singapore%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20food%20regulators%20have%20warned%20people%20against%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-singapore-hong-kong-bans-sale-of-mdh-everest-spices-5495187%5C%22%3E%20using%20four%20products%20from%20these%20two%20spice%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20alleged%20presence%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%20at%20%26quot%3Blevels%20exceeding%20the%20permissible%20limit%26quot%3B.%20Ethylene%20oxide%20has%20been%20classified%20as%20a%20'Group%201%20carcinogen'%20by%20the%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20spice%20products%20of%20MDH%20--%20Madras%20Curry%20Powder%20(spice%20blend%20for%20Madras%20Curry)%2C%20Sambhar%20Masala%20(Mixed%20Masala%20Powder)%2C%20and%20Curry%20Powder%20(Mixed%20Masala%20Powder)%20--%20along%20with%20Everest's%20Fish%20Curry%20Masala%20contain%20%E2%80%9Ca%20pesticide%2C%20ethylene%20oxide%26quot%3B%2C%20Hong%20Kong's%20Centre%20for%20Food%20Safety%20(CFS)%20said%20on%20April%205.%20The%20regulator%20instructed%20the%20vendors%20%E2%80%9Cto%20stop%20the%20sale%20and%20remove%20from%20shelves%20the%20affected%20products%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Singapore%20Food%20Agency%20(SFA)%20also%20ordered%20a%20recall%20of%20Everest's%20Fish%20Curry%20Masala%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%20at%20levels%20%E2%80%9Cexceeding%20the%20permissible%20limit%E2%80%9D.%20The%20SFA%20posted%20a%20release%20on%20its%20website%20on%20April%2018%20that%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Chas%20directed%20the%20importer%2C%20Sp%20Muthiah%20%26amp%3B%20Sons%20Pte.%20Ltd.%2C%20to%20recall%20the%20products.%20The%20recall%20is%20ongoing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20MDH%20and%20Everest%20Foods%20are%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BStrict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20ban%20on%20using%20ethylene%20oxide%20in%20food%20items%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20if%20harmful%20substances%20are%20found%20in%20Indian%20spices.%20There%20is%20a%20provision%20for%20criminal%20proceedings%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20Spices%20Board%2C%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%2C%20to%20spread%20awareness%20that%20no%20harmful%20elements%20should%20be%20added%20to%20the%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20has%20said%20it%20was%20looking%20into%20the%20ban%20imposed%20by%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20four%20spices-mix%20products%20of%20Indian%20brands.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20matter.%20We%20are%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Spices%20Board%20of%20India%20Director%20AB%20Rema%20Shree%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20insisted%20that%20they%20had%20been%20testing%20samples%20even%20before%20the%20incidents%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20and%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20no%20harmful%20elements%20have%20been%20found%20in%20the%20spices%20of%20different%20brands%20available%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20continuous%20process%20of%20sampling.%20This%20time%20we%20will%20take%20samples%20more%20quickly%20and%20in%20greater%20numbers%20than%20whatever%20samples%20we%20were%20taking%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20ethylene%20oxide%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Spices%20Board%20defines%20ethylene%20oxide%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bflammable%2C%20colourless%20gas%20at%20temperatures%20above%2010.7%20Celsius.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisinfectant%2C%20fumigant%2C%20sterilising%20agent%20and%20insecticide%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20mainly%20used%20to%20sterilise%20medical%20equipment%20and%20to%20reduce%20microbial%20contamination%20in%20spices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20produced%20from%20natural%20sources%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20generated%20from%20water-logged%20soil%2C%20manure%2C%20and%20sewage%20sludge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEthylene%20oxide's%20health%20effects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer%20(IARC)%20classifies%20ethylene%20oxide%20as%20a%20'Group%201%20carcinogen'%2C%20meaning%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Benough%20evidence%20to%20conclude%20that%20it%20can%20cause%20cancer%20in%20humans%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShort-term%20exposure%20to%20the%20carcinogen%20can%20affect%20the%20human%20central%20nervous%20system%2C%20and%20cause%20depression%20and%20irritation%20of%20the%20eyes%20and%20mucous%20membranes%20but%20prolonged%20exposure%20can%20irritate%20the%20eyes%2C%20skin%2C%20nose%2C%20throat%2C%20and%20lungs%2C%20and%20damage%20the%20brain%20and%20nervous%20system%2C%20as%20per%20the%20US%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20(EPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713791160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fbtqj1nk8_mdh-everest-masala-_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-test-samples-after-indian-spice-brands-banned-in-hong-kong-singapore-5497633%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20ordered%20food%20commissioners%20to%20collect%20samples%20of%20spices%20from%20all%20the%20manufacturing%20units%20in%20the%20country%2C%20sources%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co