stern-nagaland-peoples-organisation-boycotts-polls-6-nagaland-districts-boycott-polls-over-demand-for-separate-terr-5475948%5C%22%3ENagaland%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20experienced%20a%20boycott%20in%20some%20districts)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-lok-sabha-elections-repolling-at-11-manipur-polling-stations-after-gunfire-evms-destroyed-5486382%5C%22%3EManipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20(as%20was%20expected%20after%20last%20year's%20violence)%2C%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20(which%20typically%20sees%20high%20voter%20turnout).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20drop%20came%20despite%20several%20awareness%20campaigns%20run%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-holds-meeting-to-mitigate-risks-due-to-heatwave-5497221%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NGOs%2C%20influencers%2C%20and%20the%20media%2C%20which%20usually%20result%20in%20an%20organic%20increase%20in%20vote%20share%20by%201-1.5%25.%20In%20today's%20world%2C%20where%20social%20media%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20shaping%20opinions%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20overlook%20these%20campaigns%20and%20their%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20Low%20Turnout%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20could%20account%20for%20this%20drop%20in%20turnout.%20Heat%20waves%20are%20being%20cited%20as%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20reasons.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20the%20temperature%20at%20noon%20on%20April%2019%2C%20the%20day%20of%20voting%2C%20was%2033oC%2C%20compared%20to%20around%2029oC%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20possible%20that%20the%20rhetoric%20around%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20'Mission%20400'%20and%20slogans%20like%20%26quot%3BAayega%20to%20Modi%20Hi%26quot%3B%20instilled%20some%20complacency%20among%20BJP%20supporters.%20Conversely%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20among%20opposition%20supporters%2C%20who%20might%20perceive%20these%20elections%20as%20a%20foregone%20conclusion%20now%2C%20kept%20people%20away%20from%20polling%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%20and%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20caste%20and%20community%20issues%20may%20also%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20low%20turnout%20numbers.%20Dissatisfaction%20within%20the%20Rajput%20community%20over%20Union%20minister%20Pursushottam%20Rupala's%20statement%20and%20demands%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20his%20candidature%2C%20coupled%20with%20discontent%20within%20the%20Jat%20community%20due%20to%20the%20farmers'%20unrest%2C%20may%20have%20affected%20voting%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20remote%20polling%20mechanisms%20may%20have%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20migrant%20populations%20in%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Maharashtra%20to%20return%20to%20their%20home%20states%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%2C%20thus%20impacting%20voting%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouth%20And%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20notable%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20only%2038%25%20of%20young%20eligible%20voters%20chose%20to%20register%20themselves%20speaks%20about%20the%20disconnect%20young%20people%20feel%20with%20contemporary%20politics%20and%20politicians.%20Politics%20is%20often%20perceived%20as%20a%20dirty%20word%20among%20youngsters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20low%20turnout%20in%20urban%20centres%20like%20Chennai%20highlights%20significant%20urban%20apathy.%20Various%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20DMK%20and%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20have%20led%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20years.%20But%20none%20has%20been%20able%20to%20address%20issues%20like%20waterlogging%20and%20floods%20during%20monsoon.%20This%20casts%20doubts%20about%20the%20political%20will%20of%20these%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20capabilities%20of%20their%20leaders%20and%20the%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increasingly%20polarised%20nature%20of%20elections%2C%20marked%20by%20shrill%20campaigns%20from%20political%20parties%2C%20is%20also%20alienating%20a%20section%20of%20voters%20from%20the%20political%20process.%20In%20a%20landscape%20divided%20between%20pro-government%20and%20anti-government%20factions%2C%20there's%20little%20space%20for%20neutral%20voters.%20Moreover%2C%20none%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20has%20active%20apolitical%20community%20outreach%20programmes%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lack%20of%20mechanisms%20for%20active%20public%20participation%20in%20governance%2C%20even%20at%20the%20local%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoter%20Disconnect%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20growing%20sense%20of%20frustration%20among%20voters%20as%20politicians%20prioritise%20rhetoric%20over%20addressing%20real%20issues%20affecting%20the%20common%20man.%20The%20repetition%20of%20the%20same%20speeches%20by%20the%20top%20leadership%20across%20parties%20has%20only%20exacerbated%20this%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20indicate%20that%20this%20election%20has%20also%20seen%20a%20reduction%20in%20ground-level%20campaigning%20activities%20like%20door-to-door%20visits%2C%20small%20meetings%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enukkad%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20could%20possibly%20be%20contributing%20to%20voter%20disengagement.%20Social%20media%20discussions%20also%20point%20to%20an%20apparent%20disillusionment%20of%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20feels%20that%20it%20pays%20significant%20taxes%20but%20receives%20inadequate%20benefits%20in%20return%2C%20including%20no%20access%20to%20social%20security%20or%20coverage%20under%20schemes%20like%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20time%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20leaders%20to%20reassess%20their%20strategies%20and%20re-engage%20voters%20in%20the%20remaining%20six%20phases%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713789900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-02%2Fvoting-generic_650x400_81488189947.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-turnout-is-polarisation-pushing-people-out-of-political-process-5498331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recently%20concluded%20Phase%201%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20this%20year%20recorded%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2065.5%25%2C%20lower%20than%20the%20almost%2070%25%20turnout%20recorded%20in%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-turnout-is-polarisation-pushing-people-out-of-political-process-5498331%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-turnout-is-polarisation-pushing-people-out-of-political-process-5498331%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-turnout-is-polarisation-pushing-people-out-of-political-process-5498331%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMust%20Act%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%20To%20Poll%20Body%20Over%20PM's%20%26quot%3BWealth%20To%20Infiltrators%26quot%3B%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20approached%20the%20Election%20Commission%20demanding%20action%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20claim%20that%20the%20party%2C%20if%20brought%20to%20power%2C%20will%20redistribute%20the%20nation's%20wealth%20in%20favour%20of%20Muslims%20and%20is%20also%20eyeing%20women's%20%26quot%3Bmangalsutras%26quot%3B%20for%20this%20cause.%20The%20party%20has%20already%20vehemently%20criticised%20PM%20Modi%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%20comments%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20letter%20to%20Commission%20contained%20its%20strongest%20remarks%20in%20recent%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20have%20objections%20to%20the%20entire%20tone%20and%20tenor%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20speech%2C%20in%20this%20representation%20we%20wish%20to%20highlight%20the%20completely%20unprecedented%20and%20malicious%20allegations%20as%20well%20statements%20which%20are%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20creating%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20far%20worse%20than%20any%20ever%20made%20by%20a%20sitting%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20This%20cannot%20go%20unchecked%2C%20unanswered%20and%20unpunished%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20said%20the%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP's%20repeated%20comments%20invoking%20religious%20sentiments%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20bolstered%20by%20the%20Hon'ble%20Commission's%20inaction%26quot%3B%20in%20penalising%20them%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20and%20direct%20violations%20of%20electoral%20laws%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20PM%20had%20given%20a%20speech%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20targets%20a%20particular%20community%20which%20may%20snatch%20our%20national%20resources.%20That%20community%20is%20linked%20with%20infiltrators.%20His%20allegations%20about%20an%20attack%20on%20Mangalsutras%2C%20is%20again%20a%20religious%20link.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20a%20blatant%20violation%20of%20ECI%20circular%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20party%20leader%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20said%20after%20meeting%20the%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thankful%20to%20ECI%20to%20give%20us%20time%2C%20we%20had%20raised%2017%20issues%20which%20attacks%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20our%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20first%20raised%20the%20issue%20in%20Rajasthan%20over%20the%20weekend%20and%20then%20reiterated%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20elections%20are%20due%20later%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20he%20said%2C%20promises%20that%20if%20they%20come%20to%20power%2C%20%26quot%3Beveryone's%20property%20will%20be%20surveyed%2C%20it%20will%20calculate%20gold%20belonging%20to%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20and%20then%20redistribute%20it.%20They%20won't%20even%20spare%20your%20mangalsutra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20under%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20it%20had%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20country's%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20they%20will%20gather%20this%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20people%20who%20have%20more%20children%2C%20among%20infiltrators.%20Will%20your%20hard-earned%20money%20be%20given%20to%20infiltrators%3F%20Do%20you%20accept%20this%3F%20The%20Congress%20manifesto%20is%20saying%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713788460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fh0piqe6g_narendra-modi_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmust-act-congress-to-election-commission-over-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-remark-5497957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20has%20approached%20the%20Election%20Commission%20demanding%20action%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20claim%20that%20the%20party%2C%20if%20brought%20to%20power%2C%20will%20redistribute%20the%20nation's%20wealth%20in%20favour%20of%20Muslims.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmust-act-congress-to-election-commission-over-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-remark-5497957%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-co