2content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20his%20remarks%20at%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20property%20redistribution%20charge%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20Opposition%20party%20is%20eyeing%20the%20property%20of%20citizens%20and%20wants%20to%20loot%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Aligarh%2C%20he%20said%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20have%20lost%20all%20hope%20for%20the%20future.%20%26quot%3BThey%20question%20why%20Modi%20talks%20of%20a%20developed%20India%2C%20why%20he%20talks%20of%20making%20India%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20economy.%20These%20people%20don't%20do%20anything%20except%20for%20their%20families%20and%20their%20greed%20for%20power.%20They%20cheat%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20warn%20the%20country%20against%20Congress's%20manifesto.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20and%20INDI%20alliance%20are%20now%20eyeing%20your%20income%2C%20your%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Apparently%20referring%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress's%20prince%20has%20said%20that%20if%20they%20form%20the%20government%2C%20they%20will%20do%20investigate%20who%20earns%20how%20much%2C%20owns%20how%20much%20wealth%20and%20how%20many%20houses.%20He%20also%20says%20that%20the%20government%20will%20take%20control%20of%20your%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20everyone.%20Their%20manifesto%20says%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20which%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20referred%20to%2C%20calls%20for%20a%20nationwide%20socio-economic%20and%20caste%20census%20to%20provide%20the%20data%20foundation%20for%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Social%20Justice%20section%2C%20the%20manifesto%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20been%20th