one%20owns%20an%20ancestral%20home%20at%20the%20village%20and%20buys%20a%20flat%20in%20the%20city%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20take%20away%20one%20of%20the%20houses.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20say%20you%20already%20own%20a%20home%20and%20you%20don't%20need%20another.%20This%20is%20a%20Maoist%20mindset%2C%20a%20Communist%20mindset%2C%20they%20have%20ruined%20many%20nations.%20The%20Congress%20and%20INDI%20alliance%20want%20to%20apply%20this%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20remarks%20in%20Aligarh%20come%20a%20day%20after%20his%20comments%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20Alleging%20that%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20and%20redistribute%20private%20property%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20claimed%20that%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20under%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-manmohan-singh-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-jab-manmohan-singhs-2006-speech-a-huge-row-5495887%5C%22%3E%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20country's%20wealth.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20they%20will%20gather%20this%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20people%20who%20have%20more%20children%2C%20among%20infiltrators.%20Will%20your%20hard-earned%20money%20be%20given%20to%20infiltrators%3F%20Do%20you%20accept%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20remarks%2C%20especially%20the%20references%20to%20Muslims%2C%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmust-act-congress-to-election-commission-over-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-remark-5497957%5C%22%3EA%20Congress%20delegation%20met%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20afternoon%20and%20demanded%20strict%20action%20over%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20speech.%20Party%20leader%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20told%20the%20media%20th