ter%20issuing%20instructions%20to%20his%20government%20-%20to%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20and%20PWD%20Minister%20Atishi%20-%20from%20jail%2C%20a%20practice%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20has%20slammed%20as%20unethical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20also%20claimed%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20deliberately%20eaten%20foods%20high%20in%20sugar%20-%20mangoes%20and%20toffees%20-%20to%20elevate%20his%20blood%20sugar%20level%20and%20establish%20grounds%20for%20medical%20bail.%20The%20ED%20had%20also%20argued%20that%20mangoes%20and%20toffees%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20diet%20violated%20court%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20argument%20last%20week%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20slammed%20the%20ED%20for%20its%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20shocking%20that%20ED%20(believes)%20a%20person%20would%20deliberately%20cause%20such%20alarming%20hikes%20in%20sugar%20level%20and%20risk%20his%20life%20-%20for%20getting%20medical%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20argued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Was%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Arrested%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20on%20March%2021%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20The%20probe%20agency%20believes%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20now-scrapped%20policy%20and%20seeking%20bribes%2C%20or%20kickbacks%2C%20in%20return%20for%20liquor%20licences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20have%20refused%20all%20charges%20and%20called%20the%20arrest%20and%20case%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vendetta%26quot%3B%2C%20coming%20as%20it%20did%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20challenged%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20However%2C%20the%20top%20court%20has%20refused%20an%20early%20hearing.%20He%20must%20now%20wait%20till%20April%2029%2C%20when%20the%20court%20recon