y%20booked%20seats%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20theatre%20and%20to%20the%20side%20so%20she%20could%20make%20a%20quick%20dart%20to%20the%20exit%20if%20her%20baby%20got%20too%20rowdy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EComedy%20festival's%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Melbourne%20International%20Comedy%20Festival%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BArj%20is%20independently%20produced%20and%20at%20a%20venue%20not%20managed%20by%20the%20festival%2C%20however%2C%20any%20interaction%20between%20performers%20and%20their%20audiences%20requires%20sensitivity%20and%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20festival%20managed%20venues%2C%20babes%20in%20arms%20are%20generally%20allowed%20but%20we%20do%20ask%20people%20to%20sit%20up%20the%20back%20with%20their%20child%20so%20they%20can%20quickly%20and%20easily%20leave%20if%20the%20baby%20gets%20noisy%2C%20so%20as%20not%20to%20disturb%20the%20artist%20and%20other%20patrons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713785760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F8qs62ba_comedian-arj-barker_625x300_22_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foutrage-after-us-comedian-kicks-breastfeeding-woman-baby-out-of-his-show-5497528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20comedian%20stood%20by%20the%20decision%2C%20telling%20people%20that%20''the%20baby%20was%20disrupting%20my%20performance''%20and%20that%20he%20''politely%20told%20her%20the%20baby%20couldn't%20stay.''%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foutrage-after-us-comedian-kicks-breastfeeding-woman-baby-out-of-his-show-5497528%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foutrage-after-us-comedian-kicks-breastfeeding-woman-baby-out-of-his-show-5497528%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%2